---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Color Picker & Converter
description: Free online color picker and converter. Convert between HEX, RGB, HSL, and HSV color formats. Pick colors and generate palettes instantly.
keywords: color picker, hex to rgb, rgb to hex, color converter, hsl converter, color palette generator, hex color picker
permalink: /tools/color-picker/
toolId: color-picker
toolJs: color-picker.js
ogImage: color-picker.jpg
---
{# Get tool data from tools.json #}
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<!-- Schema.org BreadcrumbList -->
<script type="application/ld+json">
